cards.flavorText: Wings and beaks. I like yours, and I like mine, too.

cards.flavorText: This fluffiness makes everyone go crazy. Is it really that charming?

cards.name: Fletchling

attacks.text: Search your deck for up to 2 Fletchling, reveal them, and put them into your hand. Shuffle your deck afterward.

cards.flavorText: Little friends, thanks for always helping me look so cute!

cards.name: Floral Crown
rules: Attach a Pokémon Tool to 1 of your Pokémon that doesn't already have a Pokémon Tool attached to it.
At the end of your opponent's turn, heal 20 damage from the Basic Pokémon this card is attached to.

cards.name: Wally
rules: You may play only 1 Supporter card during your turn (before your attack).

Search your deck for a card that evolves from 1 of your Pokémon (excluding Pokémon-EX) and put it onto that Pokémon. (This counts as evolving that Pokémon.) Shuffle your deck afterward. You can use this card during your first turn or on a Pokémon that was put into play this turn.

cards.name: Flareon-EX

abilities.text: Once during your turn (before your attack), you may move a Fire Energy from 1 of your Pokémon to this Pokémon.

rules: Pokémon-EX rule: When a Pokémon-EX has been Knocked Out, your opponent takes 2 Prize cards.

attacks.name: Blaze Ball
attacks.text: This attack does 20 more damage for each Fire Energy attached to this Pokémon.

cards.flavorText: A yellow body is proof of good health. If you touch its bright-red cheeks, you'll see its shining, smiling face!
